data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Lorson Ranch! This stunning two-story residence offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and comfortable living.   As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by an inviting living space adorned with high-end finishes. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and elegant granite countertops, creating a stylish and functional space for culinary enthusiasts. Picture yourself preparing meals surrounded by the sleek design and modern conveniences. Upstairs, you'll find all 4 bedrooms. The master bedroom is a true sanctuary, featuring an en suite bathroom for added convenience and luxury. Imagine unwinding after a long day in your own private oasis. The home also includes a spacious 2-car garage, ensuring that your vehicles are secure and protected from the elements. Convenience is key, especially with the proximity to Fort Carson Army Base. Enjoy a short commute and spend more time at home with your loved ones. One of the highlights of this property is the newer oversized patio, perfect for entertaining guests or simply enjoying the beautiful Colorado weather. Whether you're hosting a barbecue or just relaxing with a cup of coffee, this outdoor space will quickly become a favorite spot. Lorson Ranch offers a welcoming community atmosphere, and with the added benefit of being close to Fort Carson Army Base, you'll appreciate the convenience and sense of security. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home – schedule a viewing today and envision the possibilities that await you in this exceptional property.
